</span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">function</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">update</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">{</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Save the file and your browser should <strong>auto-refresh</strong> with your Phaser game running. What kind of game are you building?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
