</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You're already set up and using it! The Phaser project you just created is proof of that.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
