<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>5. Now go back to Tiled → Browse</strong> and navigate to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/tileset.png</code></p>
