ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">OK! Let's skip Kenney for now and <strong>generate a tileset directly</strong> so you don't need to download anything. I'll create one for you right now.</p></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-1.5"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="true"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate text-sm font-base">Ran a command, read a file</span><span class="inline-flex transition-transform duration-200 shrink-0"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Ran a command, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 1fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"><div class="flex flex-col font-ui leading-normal"><div><div><div class="flex flex-col shrink-0"><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150"></div></div></div><div class="transition-colors rounded-lg duration-150"><div class="flex flex-row items-center py-1"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center shrink-0 text-text-500"><div class="text-text-500" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-text-500" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M5.146 7.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l2.5 2.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .062.631l-.062.077-2.5 2.5a.5.5 0 1 1-.708-.707L7.293 10 5.146 7.854a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708M14.5 12a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-5a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1z"></path><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.5 4A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 18 5.5v9a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-13A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 2 14.5v-9A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3.5 4zm-13 1a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v9a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h13a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5v-9a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="group/row flex flex-row items-center rounded-lg px-2.5 w-full justify-between text-text-300 cursor-pointer transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-text-200 hover:text-text-000"><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="text-sm text-text-500 text-left truncate w-0 flex-grow">Create a simple platformer tileset PNG using Python</div></div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-1.5 shrink-0"></div></button></div></div><div class="flex flex-row"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center shrink-0"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="mx-2.5 mt-1 mb-2"><div class="overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; height: auto;"><div class="rounded-lg border-[0.5px] border-border-300 bg-bg-000 cursor-pointer"><div class="p-2 flex flex-col gap-2 max-h-[200px] overflow-y-auto [&amp;_pre]:!text-xs [&amp;_code]:!text-xs"><div class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-3 bg-bg-100 rounded-md !bg-bg-100"><div class="flex justify-between items-center h-3"><p class="text-text-300 text-[0.6875rem] font-mono font-[450]">bash</p></div><div class="code-block__code !my-0 !p-0 !rounded-none !text-sm !leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code class="language-bash" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span><span>pip </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">install</span><span> Pillow --break-system-packages -q </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240);">&amp;&amp;</span><span> python3 </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240);">&lt;&lt;</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">'EOF'
</span></span><span>from PIL import Image, ImageDraw
</span><span>
</span><span># 4 tiles across, 2 rows = 8 tiles total, each 32x32
</span><span>TILE = 32
</span><span>COLS = 4
</span><span>ROWS = 2
</span><span>img = Image.new("RGBA", (TILE * COLS, TILE * ROWS), (0, 0, 0, 0))
</span><span>draw = ImageDraw.Draw(img)
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 0: Grass top (green)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([0, 0, 31, 31], fill=(106, 190, 48))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([0, 0, 31, 5], fill=(76, 153, 0))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 1: Dirt (brown)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([32, 0, 63, 31], fill=(139, 90, 43))
</span><span>for i in range(2):
</span><span>    for j in range(2):
</span><span>        draw.rectangle([32+4+i*14, 4+j*14, 32+10+i*14, 10+j*14], fill=(120, 75, 30))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 2: Stone (gray)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([64, 0, 95, 31], fill=(150, 150, 150))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([64, 0, 95, 31], outline=(100, 100, 100))
</span><span>draw.line([80, 0, 80, 31], fill=(100, 100, 100))
</span><span>draw.line([64, 16, 95, 16], fill=(100, 100, 100))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 3: Platform top (wood)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([96, 0, 127, 31], fill=(180, 120, 60))
</span><span>draw.line([96, 8, 127, 8], fill=(140, 90, 40))
</span><span>draw.line([96, 16, 127, 16], fill=(140, 90, 40))
</span><span>draw.line([96, 24, 127, 24], fill=(140, 90, 40))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 4: Sky/empty (transparent - already done)
</span><span># Tile 5: Brick
</span><span>draw.rectangle([32, 32, 63, 63], fill=(180, 60, 40))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([32, 32, 47, 47], outline=(140, 40, 20))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([48, 32, 63, 47], outline=(140, 40, 20))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([32, 48, 55, 63], outline=(140, 40, 20))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([56, 48, 63, 63], outline=(140, 40, 20))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 6: Ice (light blue)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([64, 32, 95, 63], fill=(180, 220, 255))
</span><span>draw.rectangle([64, 32, 95, 63], outline=(140, 190, 230))
</span><span>
</span><span># Tile 7: Lava (orange/red)
</span><span>draw.rectangle([96, 32, 127, 63], fill=(220, 80, 20))
</span><span>draw.ellipse([98, 34, 110, 46], fill=(255, 140, 0))
</span><span>draw.ellipse([112, 42, 124, 58], fill=(255, 140, 0))
</span><span>
</span><span>img.save("/mnt/user-data/outputs/tileset.png")
</span><span>print("Done!")
</span><span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">EOF</span><span>
</span></span><span></span></code></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-3 p-3 bg-bg-100 rounded-md !bg-bg-100"><div class="flex justify-between items-center h-3"><p class="text-text-300 text-[0.6875rem] font-ui font-medium">Output</p></div><div class="code-block__code !my-0 !p-0 !rounded-none !text-sm !leading-relaxed" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono);"><code style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240); background: transparent; font-family: var(--font-mono); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span><span>Done!
</span></span><span></span></code></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div class="flex flex-col shrink-0"><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div></div><div class="transition-colors rounded-lg duration-150"><div class="flex flex-row items-center py-1"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center shrink-0 text-text-500"><div class="text-text-500" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-text-500" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M11.586 2a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.06.44l2.914 2.914a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 .44 1.06V16.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-9a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.492-1.347L4 16.5v-13A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 5.5 2zM5.5 3a.5.5 0 0 0-.5.5v13a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h9a.5.5 0 0 0 .5-.5V7h-2.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 11 5.5V3zm7.04 10.304a.5.5 0 0 1 .92.392c-.295.69-.871 1.304-1.66 1.304-.487 0-.892-.234-1.2-.574-.309.34-.713.574-1.2.574-.486 0-.892-.233-1.2-.574-.31.34-.714.574-1.2.574a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1c.212 0 .52-.18.74-.696l.034-.067a.5.5 0 0 1 .886.067c.221.516.528.696.74.696.213 0 .52-.18.74-.696l.035-.067a.5.5 0 0 1 .885.067c.22.516.527.696.74.696s.519-.18.74-.696m0-4a.5.5 0 0 1 .92.392c-.295.69-.871 1.304-1.66 1.304-.487 0-.892-.234-1.2-.574-.309.34-.713.574-1.2.574-.486 0-.892-.233-1.2-.574-.31.34-.714.574-1.2.574a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1c.212 0 .52-.18.74-.696l.034-.067a.5.5 0 0 1 .886.067c.221.516.528.696.74.696.213 0 .52-.18.74-.696l.035-.067a.5.5 0 0 1 .885.067c.22.516.527.696.74.696s.519-.18.74-.696M12 5.5a.5.5 0 0 0 .5.5h2.293L12 3.207z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><button class="group/row flex flex-row items-center rounded-lg px-2.5 w-full justify-between text-text-300 !cursor-default"><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="text-sm text-text-500 text-left truncate w-0 flex-grow"><span class="truncate">Presented file</span></div></div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-1.5 shrink-0"></div></button></div></div><div class="flex flex-row"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center shrink-0"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="flex flex-col shrink-0"><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div></div><div class="transition-colors rounded-lg duration-150"><div class="flex flex-row"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center shrink-0"><div class="flex flex-col items-center pt-1"><div class="text-text-500" style="width: 16px; height: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-text-500" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M10 2.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 0 15 7.5 7.5 0 0 1 0-15m0 1a6.5 6.5 0 1 0 0 13 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 0-13m2.61 3.688a.5.5 0 0 1 .78.625l-4 5a.5.5 0 0 1-.661.107l-.083-.066-2-2-.064-.079a.5.5 0 0 1 .693-.693l.079.064 1.604 1.605z"></path></svg></div><div class="w-[1px] flex-1 mt-1 duration-150 bg-border-300"></div></div></div><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="pl-2.5 pt-0.5 text-text-300 !font-base">Done</div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-row h-[8px]"><div class="w-[20px] flex justify-center"><div class="w-[1px] h-full duration-150"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Download that tileset</strong> and save it into your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/</code> folder as <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset.png</code>.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Now back in Tiled, do this:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1. In the Name field type:</strong> <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset</code></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>2. Click Browse</strong> and navigate to your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/tileset.png</code></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>3. Settings:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tile width: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">32 px</code> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tile height: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">32 px</code> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Margin: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">0 px</code> ✅</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Spacing: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">0 px</code> ✅</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>4. Click Save As</strong> → save as <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset.tsx</code> into <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/</code></p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You'll then see <strong>8 tiles</strong> appear in the tileset panel — grass, dirt, stone, wood, brick, ice, and lava. Then we paint your level! 🎨</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="Tileset. Open artifact."></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M216,42H40A14,14,0,0,0,26,56V200a14,14,0,0,0,14,14H216a14,14,0,0,0,14-14V56A14,14,0,0,0,216,42ZM40,54H216a2,2,0,0,1,2,2V163.57L188.53,134.1a14,14,0,0,0-19.8,0l-21.42,21.42L101.9,110.1a14,14,0,0,0-19.8,0L38,154.2V56A2,2,0,0,1,40,54ZM38,200V171.17l52.58-52.58a2,2,0,0,1,2.84,0L176.83,202H40A2,2,0,0,1,38,200Zm178,2H193.8l-38-38,21.41-21.42a2,2,0,0,1,2.83,0l38,38V200A2,2,0,0,1,216,202ZM146,100a10,10,0,1,1,10,10A1