t-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You should see the tileset image displayed above — it shows 8 colored tiles.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>To download and use it:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Click the image</strong> shown above in the chat</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Right click it</strong> → <strong>Save image as</strong></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save it directly into your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/</code> folder</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Name it exactly <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset.png</code></li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Also to answer your other question</strong> — the code I wrote was just to <em>generate</em> the image on my end. You don't paste that code anywhere. The image itself is what you need, not the code. Just right click → save it.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Then in Tiled:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Name: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Browse to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/tileset.png</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Change tile size to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">64x64</code></strong> this time</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Save As <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">tileset.tsx</code> in <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">public/assets/</code></li>
</ul></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300/15 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="Tileset. Open artifact."></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M216,42H40A14,14,0,0,0,26,56V200a14,14,0,0,0,14,14H216a14,14,0,0,0,14-14V56A14,14,0,0,0,216,42ZM40,54H216a2,2,0,0,1,2,2V163.57L188.53,134.1a14,14,0,0,0-19.8,0l-21.42,21.42L101.9,110.1a14,14,0,0,0-19.8,0L38,154.2V56A2,2,0,0,1,40,54ZM38,200V171.17l52.58-52.58a2,2,0,0,1,2.84,0L176.83,202H40A2,2,0,0,1,38,200Zm178,2H193.8l-38-38,21.41-21.42a2,2,0,0,1,2.83,0l38,38V200A2,2,0,0,1,216,202ZM146,100a10,10,0,1,1,10,10A10,10,0,0,1,146,100Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Tileset</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opacity-100 transit